snippet.title: Incenter of a Triangle - Find Using Compass (Geometry)
snippet.description:
Learn how to construct the incenter of a triangle in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring using a compass and straightedge. We discuss this point of concurrency and the properties of the incenter.

0:08 What is the Incenter and How to Find.
0:27 How to Draw the 3 Angle Bisectors
1:53 Draw a Perpendicular from the Incenter to the Side of Triangle
2:52 Inscribe a Circle Inside of the Triangle
